    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
