    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 2 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Add your <strong>lamb mince</strong>, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go, and cook for a further 4-5 min or until starting to brown</p><p>Meanwhile, reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
