    {
      "instruction": "<p>Just before serving, mix your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a large bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and add it to the dressing, then give everything a good mix up</p>",
